00:16.141 --> 00:20.061
I'm sorry. I, uh-
[Laughing]

00:20.145 --> 00:22.605
I can't hold it in
any longer. Um-

00:23.607 --> 00:25.942
Mom, Dad,

00:27.152 --> 00:29.404
- Terri's pregnant.
- What?

00:29.488 --> 00:31.989
- It's a boy.
- [Mother]
Oh!

00:32.074 --> 00:34.492
Our first grandbaby!
[Laughing]

00:34.576 --> 00:37.036
- Oh, that's fantastic.
- Thank you.

00:37.121 --> 00:39.163
- Yeah. Sweetheart? Honey.
- Yeah?

00:39.248 --> 00:41.666
