tell anybody yet.

00:41.750 --> 00:44.377
Your secret is safe with me.
I spent six months
in the Hanoi Hilton.

00:44.461 --> 00:46.504
- Never said a word.
Am I right, Doodle?
- That's right, honey.

00:46.588 --> 00:48.715
[All Chuckling]
Oh.

00:48.799 --> 00:51.217
Yeah, we're gonna
turn the craft room
into the nursery.

00:51.301 --> 00:54.095
- Oh! Show me!
- Okay.

00:54.179 --> 00:55.847
[Father Chuckles]

00:57.474 --> 01:00.518
[Exhales]

01:00.602 --> 01:02.520
I'm really
happy for you, Son.

01:02.604 --> 01:05.356
Tell you the truth,
I'm terrified.

01:05.441 --> 01:07.358
I... don't know
how to do this.

01:07.443 --> 01:11.112
No one does.
Look at me. I was a mess.

01:11.196 --> 01:14.741
